<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.4">
<l>taḷarntiṭ ṭimaiyōr caraṇtā veṉattāṉ caraṇāy muraṇā yavaṉai yukirāl</l>
<l>piḷantiṭ ṭamarark karuḷcey tukanta perumāṉ tirumāl virinī rulakai</l>
<l>vaḷarntiṭ ṭatolcīr viṟalmā valiyai maṇkoḷ  ḷavañcit torumāṇ kuṟaḷāy</l>
<l>aḷantiṭ ṭavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇ ṇeyuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great lord who, when the suffering celestials cried,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Give us refuge,” becoming their refuge,</l>
<l>Splitting the one who was his enemy with his claws, rejoiced,</l>
<l rend="indent">bestowing grace to the immortals, Tirumāl,</l>
<l>The one who, deceiving Māvali of increased, fine, ancient fame,</l>
<l rend="indent">to take the earth, as a novice dwarf measured the wide, watered world,</l>
<l>See, he is the one who was bound, having eaten the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">churned by the herder women today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
